import img1 from "../../images/building_block.svg";
import img2 from "../../images/wash_hands.svg";
import img3 from "../../images/under_construction.svg";
import img4 from "../../images/For_sale.svg";
import img5 from "../../images/svg-5.svg";
import img6 from "../../images/svg-6.svg";

export const HomeObjOne = {
  id: "about",
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDecs: true,
  topLine: "Why us?",
  headLine: "Tassan Brother Company",
  decsription:
    "Builders come and go, but you can count on DP Construction to see you not only through, but beyond the building process. Whether you want a bathroom remodel or a new home, you need a contractor that is reliable, trustworthy, and will get the project done. ",
  buttonLabel: "Get Sarted",
  imgStart: false,
  img: img1,
  alt: "TassanCo",
  dark: true,
  primary: true,
  darkText: false,
};


export const HomeObjTwo = {
    id: "discover",
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDecs: false,
    topTitle: "Why Us",
    title: "Top Quality and long term Garanty ",
    decsription:
      "It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.",
    buttonLabel: "Learn More",
    imgStart: true,
    img: img4,
    alt: "TassanVro's",
    dark: false,
    primary: false,
    darkText: true,
  };
  
  export const HomeObjThree = {
    id: "signup",
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDecs: true,
    topTitle: "Get In Touch",
    title: "Contact us we cant wait to hear from you.",
    decsription:
      "Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. ",
    buttonLabel: "Contact Us",
    imgStart: false,
    img: img3,
    alt: "TassanCo",
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: false,
  };
  

  export const HomeObjFour = {
    id: "id4",
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDecs: false,
    topTitle: "Why Us",
    title: "Top Quality and long term Garanty ",
    decsription:
      "It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.",
